qFieldDefs:
=pick ( 

(v_Selected_Measure_Cust_Key_Name)


    
,(if 
 (
     Aggr
          ( nodistinct
                Avg({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] )
                , ([Customer], Year)
          )>=76
    ,'A - Platinum',
    
    
    if 
 (
Aggr
          ( nodistinct
                Avg({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] )
                , ([Customer], Year)
          )>=51
    ,'B - Gold',
    
    
   
        if 
 (
Aggr
          ( nodistinct
                Avg({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] )
                , ([Customer], Year)
          )>=26
    ,'C - Silver', 
    
    
    
        if 
 (
Aggr
          ( nodistinct
                Avg({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] )
                , ([Customer], Year)
          )>0
    ,'D- Bronze', 'No Score'    
    )))))

,$(V_Scoring_Tier_CustomerAccount)
,$(v_Scoring_Tier_CustomerChain)

)

pick ( 

(v_Selected_Measure_Cust_Key_Name)

,count({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  Distinct [Customer] )
,Count({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  Distinct [Customer Key] )
,count({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  Distinct [Customer Chain] )


)

pick ( 

(v_Selected_Measure_Cust_Key_Name)

,avg({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] )
,avg({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score] )
,avg({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY CHAIN] )


)

pick(

$(v_Selected_Measure_Cust_Key_Name)

,   IF( Scoring ='Platinum',


count({<
[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},  
    Customer = {'=Aggr(Avg({<[Sales Type]={"Scoring"},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] ) , ([Customer] , Year) )>=76'} ,
    
    [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, 
    Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  
    
    Distinct [Customer] )


,IF( Scoring ='Gold',
    
    count({<
[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},  
    Customer = {'=Aggr(Avg({<[Sales Type]={"Scoring"},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] ) , ([Customer] , Year) )>=51 AND Aggr(Avg({<[Sales Type]={"Scoring"},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] ) , ([Customer] , Year) ) < 76' } ,
    
    [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, 
    Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  
    
    Distinct [Customer] )


,IF( Scoring ='Silver',
    
count({<
[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},  
    Customer = {'=Aggr(Avg({<[Sales Type]={"Scoring"},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] ) , ([Customer] , Year) )>=26 AND Aggr(Avg({<[Sales Type]={"Scoring"},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] ) , ([Customer] , Year) ) <51'} ,
    
    [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, 
    Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  
    
    Distinct [Customer] ),



IF ( Scoring='Bronze' , 
count({<
[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},  
    Customer = {'=Aggr(Avg({<[Sales Type]={"Scoring"},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)} >}  [Scoring - Total Customer Score - BY NAME] ) , ([Customer] , Year) ) < 26'} ,
    
    [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, 
    Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>}  
    
    Distinct [Customer] )
    
    
,
            	IF ( Scoring ='Inactive',(Count({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'},Year= ,Quarter=,Month=,[Customer]={'=sum({1<[Month ID]={"<=$(=$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY))"},Year={$(v_Max_Year_LY)}>} [Invoice Amount USD])>0 and sum({1<[Month ID]={"<=$(=$(v_Max_Month_ID))"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}>} [Invoice Amount USD])=0'}>} Distinct [Customer])),
                	IF ( Scoring='WonBack' , Count(
{$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, Year= {$(v_Max_Year)},
[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},
[Customer WinBack] -= {'WinBack $(v_Max_Year)'},
[Customer MQP Classification] -= {'MQP $(v_Max_Year)'},
Quarter=,
Month= ,
[Customer] = {'=sum({1<[Year]={$(v_Max_Year_LY)} >} [Invoice Amount USD])=0 and sum({1<[Year]={$(v_Max_Year)} >} [Invoice Amount USD]) >0 and sum({1<[Year]={"<$(=$(v_Max_Year_LY))"} >} [Invoice Amount USD])>0 '}

>} Distinct [Customer])
 +
 Count({$< 

[Year] = {$(v_Max_Year)},
[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},
[Customer WinBack]={'Winback $(v_Max_Year)'},
[Customer] = {'=sum({1<[Year]={$(v_Max_Year)} >} [Invoice Amount USD]) >0'}

>} Distinct [Customer]),
                    	IF ( Scoring ='New Customers' , Count(
{$<
[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'},
[Customer WinBack] -= {'WinBack $(v_Max_Year)'},
[Customer MQP Classification] -= {'MQP $(v_Max_Year)'},
Year=,
Quarter=,
Month=,
[Customer]={'=sum({1<[Year]={"<$(=$(v_Max_Year))"}>} [Invoice Amount USD])=0 and (sum({1<[Month ID]={"<=$(=$(v_Max_Month_ID))"}, Year={$(v_Max_Year)} >} [Invoice Amount USD])>0)'}>}

Distinct [Customer]) + Count({$< 

[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)},
[Customer MQP Classification] ={'MQP $(v_Max_Year)'},
[Customer] = {'=sum({1<[Year]={$(v_Max_Year)} >} [Invoice Amount USD]) >0'}

>}[Customer])
,
                        	IF (Scoring ='Prospects' , ( Sum({$< [Party Type]={'Prospect'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Prospect Count])),
                            	IF ( Scoring = 'Leads' ,( Sum({$<[Party Type]={'Lead'},  [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Lead Count]))
                                )))))))))
                                                                
,IF ( Scoring ='Platinum' ,   Count({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)}  , [Scoring - Total Customer Score]  = {">=76"}>}  Distinct [Customer Key] ) ,
	IF( Scoring ='Gold'  ,   Count({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)}  , [Scoring - Total Customer Score]  = {">=51<76"}>}  Distinct [Customer Key] ),
    	IF ( Scoring ='Silver' ,   Count({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)}  , [Scoring - Total Customer Score]  = {">=26<51"}>}  Distinct [Customer Key] ),
        	IF ( Scoring='Bronze' ,  Count({<[Sales Type]={'Scoring'},Year= {$(v_Max_Year)}  , [Scoring - Total Customer Score]  = {">=0<26"}>}  Distinct [Customer Key] ),
            	IF ( Scoring ='Inactive', $(v_Customers_Lost_CY_Count),
                	IF ( Scoring='WonBack' , $(v_Periodic_WinBack_Count) + $(v_Periodic_WinBack_Flagged_Count),
                    	IF ( Scoring ='New Customers' , $(v_Customers_Totaly_New_Count) + $(v_Periodic_MQP_Count),
                        	IF (Scoring ='Prospects' , $(v_Total_Prospects_YTD),
                            	IF ( Scoring = 'Leads' ,$(v_Total_Leads_YTD)
                                )))))))))
 ,$(v_Tier_Scoring_CustomerChain_Funnel)
                                                                                                
)
